{
  "stem": "18770.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we're already in a much safer place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Plus we're not planning to stay there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So-- and now we're traveling by train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because the next part of the journey now takes us from Moscow to Vladivostok-- I think, 10 or 11 days by train, an incredible distance.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, somebody showed that to me on a map.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I think it is the equivalent-- I'm not far off-- of taking a train from New York to Los Angeles back to New York and halfway to Los Angeles again.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That's how far it is.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It's like 10,000-- I mean, enormous distance.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--ever going to end?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, well, we're in a train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, it's not cold.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We're not-- this is not I mean, snow isn't blowing in through the chinks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is a train.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Stories are being told.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, we do little drawings.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We keep it-- you know, children get restless.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We run up and down the aisles.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We do whatever children do.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But we are-- the sense is we are going toward something hopefully better and away from something that was very bad.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so we-- this train takes us to Vladivostok.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We then take a boat to Japan.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Japan, I mean, [LAUGHS] talk about exotic.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] That is really an incredible experience.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It's like the-- I know that we-- I don't know the sequence on this.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I know that we get to-- at some point, we're in Yokohama briefly.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I think we sail out of Kobe, which is another port town when we finally move on from Japan.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But we stay in Tokyo for a couple of weeks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Somehow, there must be that Underground Railroad, you know, with names being passed along.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
